                        modelFields="[text@richtext]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>AbbVie grant requests originating from the United States and Puerto Rico are managed by a centralized grant department and more information is available at grants.abbvie.com.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>AbbVie discloses donations and grants made by the company because we are committed to sharing our commitment to promote health education and charitable causes that ultimately benefit patients.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>The list of AbbVie’s grants and contributions are provided in the annual report below. AbbVie’s report reflects&amp;nbsp;educational grants, patient support, charitable donations, as well as fellowships and scholarships. The report includes individual direct payments of more than $200 from AbbVie’s US and Puerto Rico businesses.&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;strong>Annual Report&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;strong>&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.abbvie.com/content/dam/abbvie-com2/pdfs/grants/2024-AbbVie-Grants-and-Contributions-Report.pdf&quot; title=&quot;&quot;>2024&lt;/a>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;em>AbbVie officially became a company January 1, 2013. In May 2020, AbbVie completed the acquisition of Allergan and began operating as a combined company.&lt;/em>&lt;/p>"/>
